customize_hero_title=Create Your Signature Fragrance
customize_hero_desc=Freely blend from dozens of notes to create your unique personal scent
customize_step1_title=Choose Base Style
customize_step1_desc=Select your preferred base from classic styles like floral, oriental, woody, oceanic
