customize_notes_title=Fragrance Notes Guide
customize_notes_desc=Understanding the three-layer structure to help you make better choices
customize_notes_top_title=Top Notes
customize_notes_top_full=The first impression of a fragrance, immediately perceptible upon spraying. Typically composed of light, fresh notes like citrus, lavender, mint, etc. Lasts approximately 15-30 minutes.
customize_notes_mid_title=Heart Notes
customize_notes_mid_full=The soul of the fragrance, emerging after the top notes fade. Typically composed of floral, fruity notes, forming the main body of the scent. Lasts approximately 2-4 hours.
customize_notes_base_title=Base Notes
customize_notes_base_full=The most enduring part of the fragrance, providing depth and longevity. Typically composed of woody notes, musk, amber, etc. Can last for hours or even all day.
customize_bottles_title=Elegant Bottles
customize_bottles_desc=Choose your favorite bottle to perfectly present your signature fragrance
customize_bottle_free=Free
customize_faq_title=FAQ
customize_faq_q1=How long does custom fragrance take?
customize_faq_a1=Custom fragrances require 3-5 business days for blending and production, then shipped via SF Express, typically arriving in 2-5 days.
customize_faq_q2=Can custom fragrances be returned?
customize_faq_a2=Since custom fragrances are specially blended based on your personal selections, returns are not supported for non-quality issues. If there are quality issues with the product, please contact customer service within 7 days of receipt.
customize_faq_q3=How long does the fragrance last?
customize_faq_a3=Our fragrances use high-quality essences, typically lasting 6-8 hours. Actual duration may vary based on skin type, environment temperature, and other factors.
customize_faq_q4=How do I choose the right notes?
customize_faq_a4=We recommend choosing based on your preferences and occasions: fresh floral or oceanic for daily use; rich oriental for dates or evening events; reserved woody for professional settings.
